{
  "1811990": {
    "name": "雪居之地 (Wildfrost)",
    "steam_appid": 1811990,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/6a69ff7bd37c268550855842fb460940.webp?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=48 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/092b0bd0f1ad8d6eb3f430c9f95cfa96.poster.avif?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/092b0bd0f1ad8d6eb3f430c9f95cfa96.webm?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/092b0bd0f1ad8d6eb3f430c9f95cfa96.mp4?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/f4a78555548b97506b93ada3403ec5b0.webp?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=59 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随着最后一缕阳光消逝……</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界被狂霜吞噬。如今，只剩雪居城中的幸存者仍坚守着人们最后的庇护所，对抗无尽寒冬……　完善你的卡牌战斗和牌组构建能力，踏上驱散《雪居之地》无尽寒冬的征程！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/d8c0ad00451399880e1b70cdc0cff771.poster.avif?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/d8c0ad00451399880e1b70cdc0cff771.webm?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/d8c0ad00451399880e1b70cdc0cff771.mp4?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择最初的部落领袖，获得各种随机技能与属性，谨慎选择路线，在寒风凛冽的冻原废土展开冒险。搭救旅途中遭遇的落难英雄，并将他们收入麾下；挖掘失落宝藏、积累财富找旅行商人购买各种物品！你每次的抉择与决策会帮你打造出独一无二的强力牌组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/ff219fd2f74538d0e58f1fb9810fb71d.poster.avif?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/ff219fd2f74538d0e58f1fb9810fb71d.webm?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/ff219fd2f74538d0e58f1fb9810fb71d.mp4?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集各式各样战力强大的卡牌英雄，以及各种方便易用的装备与配件，帮助自己进行战斗。尝试不同的元素组合，找出自己喜爱的最佳方案！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄卡牌不再是用完即丢的炮灰！不断升级、定制你的英雄，为他们装配护符吊坠、提升战力，可以为你的牌组赋予无比强大（或是无比可爱）的力量！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/f5e663c0267304c09c9a3b46cbcf0d12.poster.avif?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/f5e663c0267304c09c9a3b46cbcf0d12.webm?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/f5e663c0267304c09c9a3b46cbcf0d12.mp4?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用刺激好玩的计数系统，谋定而后动、击退敌人。《雪居之地》的战斗采用回合制，但无法在每回合都进行攻击。使用卡牌需遵循“计数”系统，计数回合结束后才能展开行动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随时留意敌方计数，提前制定战术。强化我方？干扰敌方？或是加快我方计数！如何在战场上施展战术、力挽狂澜？一切由你做主！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/7cd02f0eb508fe4183e8a7cbc6ff4948.poster.avif?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/7cd02f0eb508fe4183e8a7cbc6ff4948.webm?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/7cd02f0eb508fe4183e8a7cbc6ff4948.mp4?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想稍事休息？来温暖舒适的雪居城歇歇脚吧。幸存者们齐聚在巨型热冰——“光之结晶”周围，用它的能量取暖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你在征程中不断取得进展，雪居城的规模也会不断扩大，更可建造宠物商店、发明者小屋等建筑！新区域会解锁有趣又实用的道具供你在冒险中使用，还会为你带来新的卡牌、部落、外观、游戏挑战，以及各种遭遇事件！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/d48a9c4d08462ab3fb5bcbb97b446b87.poster.avif?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/d48a9c4d08462ab3fb5bcbb97b446b87.webm?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/d48a9c4d08462ab3fb5bcbb97b446b87.mp4?t=1765548750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就算已经战胜寒霜，但《雪居之地》的丰富内容也不会就此结束！快来参与每日征程与每日挑战，磨炼技艺、挑战最高分吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/84bedc610b6f88adcc8e4d59902f4b65.webp?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=44 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811990/extras/b6da2a108abf01b677d6a98713f3e1f9.avif?t=1765548750\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p>",
